and it won’t feel like work!</i><br></div></div></div><div id="i32"><div id="i33"><div id="i34"><div>I love my job! I love it so much that I don’t even like calling it a job. Jobs are boring and draining and often maddening.</div><div><br></div><div>I get to do what I am. So I wake up every morning and thank God for giving me these wonderful opportunities to help people.</div><div><br></div><div>It hasn’t always been like this. I used to have the typical life where I worked at the typical job and felt my soul being numbed into oblivion.</div><div><br></div><div>Current research shows that there are <b>three things</b> that motivate people to achieve extraordinary things in their lives:</div><div><br></div><div><ol><li><b>Autonomy<br></b></li><li><b>Mastery<br></b></li><li><b>Purpose</b><br></li></ol></div><div><br></div><div>But most jobs don’t provide any of these things.</div><div><br></div><div>If you find yourself wanting more out of life than just the same old thing, day after day, contact us. We can help you find a way to do what you love so that what you do will never feel like work again.</div></div></div></div><div id="pre-footer"><div id="pre-footer0"><img src="images/ACSMMemberWebID.gif" style="width: 100%; height: auto;"></div></div><div id="footer"><div id="footer0">Copyright © <span class="year">2018</span> Life Changing Coaching. All Rights Reserved.</div></div></div><script type="text/javascript">document.body.onload = deferFonts;setTimeout(deferFonts, 2000);function deferFonts() { var defer = document.querySelectorAll("[defer]"); for (var i = 0; i < defer.length; i++) { defer[i].setAttribute("href", defer[i].getAttribute("defer")); }}</script><script type="text/javascript">var vcHost = document.location.protocol == "https:" ? "https:" : "http:";document.write(unescape("%3Cscript src='" + vcHost + "//www.vcita.com/widgets/active_engage/f99c352a/loader.js' async='true' type='text/javascript'%3E%3C/script%3E"));var menuBtn = document.getElementById("me